DANGER: THIS IS IN EARLY DEVELOPEMENT !

Note:
	currently only works when taglib can correcly decode tag,
	especially for id3v1, and conversion string needs to be ended with
	utf-8,ascii

Example:
	bsdtagconv 'utf-8,ascii:zhtw:zhtw_words:utf-8,ascii' blah.mp3

Dependencies:
	bsdconv-4.9 (or 4.X && bsdconv.h fix for C++)
	audio/taglib (http://developer.kde.org/~wheeler/taglib.html)
